          %ul
            %li
              The system (web app) simulated that two seperate tasks, emails some data and emailing a list of data in CSV format. I was to arrange that the user didn't have to wait for the page to load in order to get the emails
        %li
          Run bracket's validation
          %ul
            %li I was to validate that brackets ({} []) where matched, nested properly and not empty... I was to do this with a set of validations set at the model... I was also told that Regular Expressions would not work.
        %li
          Implement a comment feature
          %ul
            %li I was to set up a comments feature, and that the users of the system could only make one comment on each of the objects, the user would have to delete the comment in order to create another one (or edit their pre-existing comment).
        %li
          Run an sql query based on the comment system in the previous task.
          %ul
            %li I was to create a page where the top 10 commenters would be listed for the previous seven days.
      Needless to say, I was excited to tackle the tasks, and I figured that I had four days (Friday afternoon to Saturday (1) Saturday to Sunday (2) Sunday to Monday (3) Monday to Tuesday (I was told Midnight day four)). It was end of day Friday, and I didn't want to bother the recruiter as it was the beginning of the weekend, so off to work I went.
